OL,3,CKing approves appointment of new
OL,4,CBishop of Durham
OL,6,FDowning Street has announced that the
OL,7,FKing has approved the appointment of
OL,8,Fthe Venerable Rick Simpson as the next
OL,9,FBishop of Durham.
OL,11,FCurrently Archdeacon of Auckland, Rick
OL,12,Fwill succeed the Right Reverend Paul
OL,13,FButler who retired from the role in
OL,14,FFebruary 2024.
OL,16,FArchdeacon Rick said: "I am humbled
OL,17,Fand delighted to have been called to
OL,18,Fbe the Bishop of this diocese, which I
OL,19,Flove.
