OL,6,F"My deepest hope is to be able to walk
OL,7,Falongside and encourage our local
OL,8,FChristian communities as they seek to
OL,9,Fboth show God's love in action and
OL,10,Fhelp people to come to life-changing
OL,11,Ffaith in Christ ` and through this see
OL,12,Four churches grow.
OL,14,F"It is also an honour to be tasked
OL,15,Fwith representing the needs and voices
OL,16,Fof people in this region in the
OL,17,Fnational church and the House of
OL,18,FLords."
