OL,3,CKing approves appointment of new
OL,4,CBishop of Durham
OL,6,FThe Right Reverend Sarah Clark, Bishop
OL,7,Fof Jarrow, is Acting Bishop of Durham
OL,8,Fin the interim. Last month Bishop
OL,9,FSarah was announced as the next Bishop
OL,10,Fof Ely.
OL,12,FBishop Sarah Clark welcomed the
OL,13,Fnomination of Archdeacon Rick who she
OL,14,Fdescribed as someone who "already
OL,15,Floves the people, parishes and
OL,16,Fcommunities of Durham Diocese and the
OL,17,FNorth East."
