OL,6,FShe added: "The voice he will bring to
OL,7,Fthe wider church and national roles
OL,8,Fwill be shaped by his long experience
OL,9,Fof the challenges and joys of life and
OL,10,Ffaith in this land of Cuthbert, Bede
OL,11,Fand Hild."
OL,13,FRick has served in the Diocese of
OL,14,FDurham since 2006 when he came to be
OL,15,FPriest in Charge of St Brandon's,
OL,16,FBrancepeth.
OL,18,FHe became Archdeacon of Auckland in
OL,19,FFebruary 2018.
