OL,11,FHe served previously in the Diocese of
OL,12,FNewcastle where, as Vicar of Holy
OL,13,FTrinity Jesmond, he saw the church
OL,14,Fgrow strongly in number and
OL,15,Fdiscipleship over ten years.
OL,17,FThe Archbishop of York, Stephen
OL,18,FCottrell said: "Archdeacon Rick has
OL,19,Fserved the Diocese of Durham with
OL,20,Fdedication over many years.
